.\\ A, {\\bf 78}, 052510 (2008)] to ensure the efficient calculation of all\nbound levels supported by a potential, including those lying extremely close to\ndissociation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 29 Sep 2011 13:26:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-30"}
