 obtained allow us to\nestimate the stored energy of the wave field in the Indian Ocean and the scales\nof its variability; to establish a positive 12-year trend of the averaged wave\nheight (about 1% per year) and wave energy (2% per year); to determine features\nof the probability distribution; and to describe the statistical properties of\nthe wave field in the zones of the Indian ocean.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 29 Sep 2011 14:31:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-09-30"}
